Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:01.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:03.86,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tempat tujuan kami adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.86,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bagian belakang apartemen Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:10.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:12.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Semua kucingnya tidak takut dengan orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.29,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kucing hitam, kucing hitam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:23.24,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Terserahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita ambil dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi ganti settingnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bukan hitam, sih...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi tidak ada pilihan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:31.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:33.01,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia sekarang temanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.48,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang akrab, ya!
