Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:44.10,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Pengambilan gambar kembali dilanjutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.18,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya tempat bukan lagi masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:48.95,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, serang Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:52.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Terimalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:55.74,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yak, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:59.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita buat kucing ini bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.46,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Namanya juga kucing peliharaan penyihir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Supaya bisa mengejek orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bukan masalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:07.35,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Namamu adalah Shamisen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:08.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo, Shamisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.77,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Katakan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.78,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan kuharap tidak akan bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.78,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Lho, Shamisen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.32,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Cukup bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:22.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kyon, aku percayakan kucing itu untuk kau pelihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:24.21,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bawa dia ke rumah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.57,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan ajari dia beberapa hal sampai besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:28.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Misalnya melompati lingkaran api.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:32.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Baik, hari ini sampai disini!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:35.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Besok akan kita jadikan klimaksnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:38.05,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Pengambilan gambarnya sempurna dan semuanya masih bugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.30,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Semuanya istirahat yang cukup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.84,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Demi hari esok!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.69,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti capek.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:58.18,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Nanti aku siapkan makanan kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Atau mau sarden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang mana saja tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:09.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, oi, tadi Nagato, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tanya kucing, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Memang itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:15.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebagai jawaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Apa aku salah bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.58,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mengejutkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.27,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kucing jantan tiga warna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.52,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak, masalahnya bukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:28.52,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kucingnya bisa bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:35.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu kenapa kalian terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.33,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kucing setan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.47,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Titisan Nekomata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:44.86,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tentu untuk kalian aku seperti mengeluarkan suara yang menyerupai kata-kata manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jika demikian...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:49.13,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Apa kalian bisa meyakinkan diri kalian bahwa kata-kata yang kuucapkan 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:52.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,adalah sesuatu yang memiliki arti sama dengan hal yang ingin kalian dengar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.06,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Karena kau menjawab pertanyaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:03:05.04,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,1,1,0,,Apa bukan karena aku secara kebetulan mengeluarkan suara yang sesuai dengan kondisi sama dengan jawaban pertanyaanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dengan penegasanmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:10.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau menyatakan bahwa manusia bisa berbicara tanpa percakapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya, memang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.78,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Walaupun ada dua subjek yang berbicara bersama seakan melakukan kontak sosial...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi apakah mereka mengalami komunikasi efektif secara mutual...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.41,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.30,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Karena mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak mengatakan maksud yang mereka simpan untuk suatu kondisi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.15,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Diem aja, napa luh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.44,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya memang seperti itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.09,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Maafkan saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bisakah anda tutup mulut juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:39.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Keadaannya tidak terlalu baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita masih...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Terlalu meremehkan Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.00,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Set dari film Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:54.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menjadi media pengubah identitas dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.55,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jika dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:59.06,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Berpikir untuk merekam adegan saat ada meteor raksasa jatuh dari langit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:01.40,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mungkin akan terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lalu kita harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita mencegah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Supaya fiksi dan realita tidak bercampur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:11.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia saat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Secara tidak sadar tengah mencampuradukkan kenyataan dan fiksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.40,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia sedang tersangkut dalam kesenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.40,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kemampuan tak diketahui milik Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.32,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menjadi filter dalam pembuatan film ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebagai materi pembangunnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebagai pencegahannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.95,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita harus membuat Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.87,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mengerti bahwa semua ini hanya fiksi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:32.40,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan membuatnya menuntun alur film ini ke jalur standar rasional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan bagaimana bisa kita membetulkan kucing yang bisa bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:38.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bermaksud membetulkannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi pada akhirnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.35,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dunia dimana kucing bisa bicara akan tercipta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.20,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yaitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Di dunia kita, dimana hal itu adalah mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.44,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lalu bagaimana dengan kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sejak awal, keberadaan kami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.79,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah berkat Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Seperti kucing berbicara itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Apa tidak ada yang bisa kita lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.62,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jika ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.46,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah dunia fantasi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.14,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Maka tidak ada penjelasan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:03.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.79,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Baik kucing berbicara dan Mikuru Beam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.54,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menjadi nyata dalam sekejap...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.92,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Artinya dunia kita akan berubah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dari dunia tanpa fenomena supernatural...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ke dunia dengan fenomena supernatural...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.82,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Secara terusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lalu kita harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita harus membuat Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Percaya bahwa semua itu hanya ada di film.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.85,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.33,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bisa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebuah teori sederhana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang mengubah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.21,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Semua kejadian tidak masuk akal menjadi fenomena lumrah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.94,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.74,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.08,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir Haruhi akan menelan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mungkin akan sulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.33,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Keadaan ini sebaiknya diselesaikan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dengan meyakinkan bahwa semua yang ada dalam film...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:52.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah mimpi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kebohongan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.72,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Juga kebetulan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah penyebab semua keganjilan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menurutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Mungkin untukmu memang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Mungkin untukku juga begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.86,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.85,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Di rumah jangan bicara apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bertingkahlah kekucingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.32,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku masih tidak tahu yang kau maksud dengan "Kekucingan"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi akan kulakukan sesuai yang kau katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.37,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jangan bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.13,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau jawab bilang saja "Meong".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.47,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Meong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.02,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kucing, kucing, kucing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:37.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Meong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:45.85,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sampai nanti, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.05,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.14,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sampai festival budaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Hanya tersisa beberapa hari lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi seperti berhubungan dengan tensi Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.84,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Keadaan ribut yang amburadul...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.81,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kini tercipta di lingkungan sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.06,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita harus cepat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:03.15,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita harus temukan Batu Kristal Bintang Legenda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:03.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.27,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yoi, yoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dalam festival ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kalau ada satu atau dua penembus dimensi berbaur...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.58,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Rasanya tidak akan aneh lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.28,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kyon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mikuru bilang dia mau bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo, Mikuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Berikan pada Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.92,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ini, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.00,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Voucher diskon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.27,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk acara kelas kami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kedai yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Silahkan bawa teman juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:35.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Cuma itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kyon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.21,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.39,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang kukatakan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.57,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Seperti menjelek-jelekkan Koizumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.47,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bukan seperti itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.37,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Memiliki pemikiran lain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Singkatnya, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.94,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.02,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sangat berbeda dengan pemahaman Koizumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:17.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tentang Haruhi itu Tuhan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:26.90,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Suzumiya-san memang benar memiliki kemampuan mengubah saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:31.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak berpikir bahwa dia juga mengubah seluruh struktur dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dunia ini sejak awal sudah begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.40,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.48,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Pandangan yang benar-benar menolak pandangan Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato-san juga sepertinya memiliki pemikiran sendiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:44.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:48.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mugkin aku tidak pantas mengatakan hal ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Semua kata-kata Koizumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.66,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.41,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya jangan dipercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.77,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu aku salah bilang begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:58.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:03.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Penjelasanku rumit karena banyak batasan hal yang bisa kusampaikan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.20,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bukankah tidak mungkin Haruhi itu Tuhan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.74,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lebih bisa memahami pandangan Asahina-san daripada Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:22.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.63,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak menentang pandangan Koizumi-kun secara pribadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.03,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jadi tolong pahami juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:35.20,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dalil yang dianut Asahina Mikuru adalah seperti berikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.26,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Suzumiya Haruhi bukanlah pencipta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Melainkan dunia sudah ada sejak awal dengan bentuk aslinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Keberadaan esper, penyimpangan waktu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Juga organisme asing berbentuk konsepsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.03,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sudah ada sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.72,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Peran Suzumiya Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah untuk menemukan mereka tanpa menyadari identitas mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan kemampuannya itu sudah dimilikinya sejak tiga tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:00.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Walaupun sanggup mengenali ketidak-normalan di dunia ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.77,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak bisa menerimanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Karena kesadaran untuk penerimaan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.10,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Masih ada disini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.28,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yaitu kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jadi Asahina-san dan Koizumi berbeda pandangan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.94,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Akibat gangguan Haruhi yang mencari fenomena ganjil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:18.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Demi melindungi ruang waktu tempat dia datang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.74,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia bersinggah di garis tengah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:28.18,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya dia baru mengatakan sesuatu yang penting diluar kebiasaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.82,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi Itsuki dan Asahina Mikuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa saling menerima pendapat lawan pihak mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.71,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Teori yang pihak mereka percayai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.13,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah goncangan besar bagi fondasi tiap pihak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:45.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi bilang dia mendapat kemampuannya tiga tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.54,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kata-kata Koizumi Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak memiliki jaminan bahwa itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.73,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Memang tidak ada jaminan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.20,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Teori Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:58.95,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Hanya kebetulan sesuai dengan apa yang kubutuhkan sebagai penjelasan dari apa yang terjadi padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.39,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang tahu kalau itu benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Begitu juga dengan teori Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.63,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Apakah versi Asahina-san itu benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.47,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang bisa menjaminnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.06,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dulu kau bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kemungkinan swa-evolusi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.62,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sejujur apapun aku padamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.92,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa membuktikannya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.09,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.94,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Karena bukti yang menjamin bahwa kata-kataku bisa dipercaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sama sekali tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.72,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untukmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:45.74,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tidak mengerti...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.47,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Orang lain juga mana bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:51.62,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Harus belajar menjelaskan dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:52.82,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Tidak akan kuserahkan batu ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:59.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Yang menganggap pengambilan gambar berjalan mulus cuma Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.48,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Aku, Koizumi dan Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sedikit demi sedikit menunjukkan ekspresi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.39,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Suram yang kian menanjak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.62,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Entah sejak kapan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.62,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Pistol model tidak menembakkan pelor BB...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.02,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Melainkan peluru air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.10,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Asahina-san juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.78,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Memakai contact beda warna lain dari Haruhi lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.78,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan menembakkan benda-benda berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:20.55,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan acap kalinya digigit oleh Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Juga sakura yang sudah mekar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Mendadak berguguran beberapa hari kemudian!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.29,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Merpati putih yang ada di kuil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:28.04,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Berubah menjadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.04,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Merpati penjelajah yang sudah lama punah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.20,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Semua gerakan Bumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.88,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya sudah rusak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.87,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kyon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.63,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ada teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.13,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.61,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.46,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Set penjelas dan alur cerita sekunder itu tidak penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:00.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak punya kesempatan memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.33,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mungkin film ini tidak akan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.69,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan itu gawat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kegawatan yang ditimbulkan oleh fiksinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.41,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah teori kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.03,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Perasaan sebenarnya Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.87,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan teori yang kita pikirkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:24.55,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bukan hanya menjadi pusat Organisasiku dan pihak wakilan Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.87,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi ada banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:30.55,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebut saja kami sedang berada...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.26,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dalam peperangan berdarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk menutupi apa yang tidak kami tampilkan di permukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.84,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Persatuan dan pengkhianatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.60,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menghalangi dan menipu satu sama lain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kehancuran dan pembunuhan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.85,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebagai cengkraman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk selamat menggunakan kekuatan masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.39,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.49,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Hal ini tidak ada hubungannya denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk Suzumiya-san juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:55.14,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Terutama Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya tidak pernah mengetahui ini selamanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.05,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak ingin melukai hatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menurutku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.49,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Suzumiya-san adalah karakter yang manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan tentunya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:10.66,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.41,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau memberitahuku itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Cuma kelepasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.95,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Apapun itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.88,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ini pembicaraan yang membosankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Memang tidak menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.57,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Masih ada satu lagi pembicaraan membosankannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.37,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bertindak diantara kau dan aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi apa alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Karena perannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Adalah untuk membujukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Orang yang akan didengarkan oleh Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.46,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak lain hanya seorang hanya kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia berada di dekatmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk memastikan kau mengambil tindakan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Penampilannya yang kekanakan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:55.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan harus merasakan penderitaan dari perintah aneh Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.77,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebagai korban yang malang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Semuanya untuk menarik perhatianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku muak dengan lawakanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.13,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak berbakat menyampaikan lawakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.26,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau kira aku bersungguh-sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.30,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Film Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.92,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan drama kelasku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tekanannya cukup kejam untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.57,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan jika Pengasingan muncul sebagai puncaknya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku mungkin akan semaput.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.05,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku minta bantuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.69,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tolong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.79,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Hentikan semua fenomena...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.41,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang muncul akibat film ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.48,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Menyadarkan Haruhi bahwa semua hal dalam film hanya pura-pura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan meyakinkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.36,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.92,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan menjelaskan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.28,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Supaya dia sadar sepenuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.01,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jika bisa sebelum semuanya selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.18,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Apa dia mau menimpakan tanggung jawab padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.46,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.06,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa membiarkannya juga, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dasar sial, sialan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Film ya film...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.09,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kenyataan ya kenyataan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Antara dua hal yang jelas berbeda itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:37.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana aku bisa membuat mereka lebih jelas berbeda lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Koizumi bilang yakinkan bahwa semuanya cuma mimpi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.32,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi selain itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Keesokannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:57.00,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku memberi saran pada Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.32,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan setelah perdebatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yak, oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.42,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dengan ini semua pengambilan gambar selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.72,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Semuanya sudah kerja keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.90,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Besok kita kumpul di ruang klub...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.44,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk melihat hasil jadinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.02,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.90,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Masih terlalu cepat untuk menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:17.88,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Simpan air mata itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.32,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Untuk Palm de Or atau Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.94,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mari kita rayakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.82,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Pertarungan terakhir Mikuru dan Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Berakhir dengan kebangkitan tiba-tiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.26,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dari kekuatan milik Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Yang entah bagaimana cara pakainya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.35,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dikirim ke sudut angkasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.36,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan terkurung selamanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Gitu doang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya selesai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.40,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Saat selesai rasanya semua terlalu cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Mikuru-chan, sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Eh, Suzumiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.03,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Waktu terasa cepat jika kita bersenang-senang...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.90,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Kenapa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:49.83,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Masalahnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.06,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang bersenang-senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sisanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.02,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bisa aku serahkan padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ada banyak hal yang harus kuingat untuk drama kelasku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Berbeda dengan film...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada pengulangan jika aku salah baca kalimat dalam prakteknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:09.81,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.72,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Satu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.08,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ucapan terima kasih untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:14.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dari Kami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.67,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan aku pribadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang keras!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tujuan kami Holywood dan Blockbuster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Demi Beruang Emas dan Singa Emas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sekarang tunjuk masa depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.44,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Nasib, nasib...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.79,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.79,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sampai akhir aku masih tidak tahu barang satu pixel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Film apa yang ingin Haruhi buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.65,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan jelasnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:47.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Waktu dan kemampuan untuk membuat visual efek...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Walaupun kau cari kemana-mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.12,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dari awal juga tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.37,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan Haruhi menggerutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:57.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak bisa menayangkan film setengah jadi begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.00,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lakukan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Festival budayanya besok, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ini jelas deadline!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.72,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau bergadang sempat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau selesaikan saja sepanjang malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.24,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku bantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Kasih yang "Wow" gitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dia bilang bantu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi Haruhi sama sekali tidak berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan akhirnya aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Ketiduran setelah beberapa saat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:33.90,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bangun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jadi, bagaimana hasilnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada artinya bergadang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Filmnya masih godokan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku datang...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.19,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dari masa depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.86,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lumayan, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.48,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Walaupun agak kurang...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.21,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau hebat juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.29,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bukan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.18,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi perbuatan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.48,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tersangka utama: Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.71,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Pesaing: Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.94,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Diluar kemungkinan: Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Pemanis: Karakter lain yang belum muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kira-kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.24,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana editingnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.85,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.21,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jelas selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.79,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Cucuran keringat dan air mata...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.57,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yang spektakuler!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.88,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sekarang ayo kita nonton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.82,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mikuru-chan, kau hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.76,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau akan menarik perhatian penonton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.69,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Selamat! Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:50.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Festival budaya dimulai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:52.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan aku tidak perlu melakukan apa-apa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.24,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Semua perubahan realita yang ditakuti sudah berakhir, sepertinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.78,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Shamisen berhenti bicara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan aku baru tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.84,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Dan soal tidak ada...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.96,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sepanjang festival budaya tidak ada yang kulihat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:10.31,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Acara dimana pesertanya berjalan-jalan memakai kostum aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.16,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Film itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.90,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Diisi dengan narasi Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.24,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Aku meyakinkannya bahwa ini tugasnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.25,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sebagai sutradara untuk membacakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.95,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Film ini adalah fiksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:29.34,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kata-kata ajaib yang menggagalkan segalanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.27,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada hubungannya dengan kejadian nyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:30.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Nama, kesatuan, acara atau fenomena lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.22,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Semuanya pura-pura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Jika ada yang sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.01,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Itu hanya kebetulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.87,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Oh, CMnya beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.04,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Semoga sukses untuk Toko Elektronik Oomori dan Toko Model Yamatsuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:42.75,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Silahkan sibukkan mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Sekali lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.87,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Film ini adalah fiksi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.45,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada hubungannya dengan kejadian nyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:55.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Ats,,0,0,0,,Kyon, kenapa aku harus mengatakan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:02.43,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Masalah ketidak-adaan masalah adalah masalah untuk Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:06.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Bisa disebut singkat, "Dunia terlalu normal".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Yang dianggapnya "Tidak normal"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.37,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:13.49,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Pastinya sesuatu yang sangat supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.51,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Berarti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.55,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,"Di depan mataku..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:18.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,"Kenapa tidak ada satu hantupun yang muncul?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:20.29,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Mungkin itulah yang ada dalam pikirannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:24.17,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ada yang harus kusampaikan, jadi dengarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:25.64,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:26.80,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:31.27,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Pernah berharap untuk bertemu alien, penjelajah waktu, atau esper, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:32.37,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Iya, sih...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.01,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Memangnya kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:34.77,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:37.18,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Alien, penjelajah waktu dan esper...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya ada didekatmu, lebih dekat dari dugaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:42.93,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, dimana dan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:44.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:48.85,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, Mikuru-chan dan Koizumi-kun, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:50.30,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Bukan "Lebih dekat dari dugaanku" lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:55.99,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Memang benar begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:02.08,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:04.89,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin itu benar-benar terjadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:10.26,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir senormal mungkin, memang benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Lalu, siapa jadi apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:15.86,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Buka kupingmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:18.09,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato Yuki adalah alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.46,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia berasal dari Himpunan-apalah-apalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.77,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dan mereka yang mengirimnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:23.38,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Humanoid interface, katanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Gitu, tuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:29.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kalau Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:31.35,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Asahina-san itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:32.69,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Cukup mudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:34.23,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia penjelajah waktu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:35.52,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia datang dari masa depan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:36.98,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jadi dia penjelajah waktu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:39.07,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Datang dari kapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:40.68,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:42.58,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.50,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Aku paham...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:47.97,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Kau paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:49.04,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Berarti...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:51.59,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-kun esper, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:53.24,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Itu maksudmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.08,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:56.11,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Memang itu yang mau kukatakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:06.70,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.21,0:24:12.91,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Cewek bloon ini....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:15.53,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau baru berpikir rasional kalau waktunya salah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.09,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau percaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.09,0:24:20.56,Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu - Default Alternative,,0,0,0,,Semuanya bisa lebih gampang!
